<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>授权跳转成功</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; 
            background: #f8fafc; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            min-height: 100vh; 
            margin: 0; 
        }
        .card { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 2.5rem; 
            border-radius: 16px; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); 
            max-width: 600px; 
            width: 90%; 
        }
        h1 { 
            color: #10b981; 
            margin-bottom: 1rem; 
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            gap: 0.5rem; 
        }
        p { color: #475569; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .params { 
            background: #f1f5f9; 
            padding: 1.25rem; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            font-family: monospace; 
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; 
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem; 
        }
        .param-item { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .param-label { color: #64748b; font-weight: bold; width: 80px; display: inline-block; }
        .tip { 
            padding: 1rem; 
            background: #f0f9ff; 
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; 
            font-size: 0.9rem; 
            color: #1e40af; 
            margin-bottom: 2rem; 
            line-height: 1.5; 
        }
        .actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }
        .btn-test { 
            background: #0f172a; 
            color: white; 
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-weight: 500; 
            font-size: 0.95rem; 
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            color: #64748b; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            align-self: center; 
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>
            <svg width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg> 
            授权跳转成功！
        </h1>
        <p>应用已接收到来自畅捷通开放平台的回调数据：</p>
        <div class="params">
            <div class="param-item"><span class="param-label">Org ID:</span> <strong style="color: #0f172a;"><%= locals.orgId || '未知' %></strong></div>
            <% if (locals.tokenData && (tokenData.userId || tokenData.user_id)) { %>
            <div class="param-item"><span class="param-label">User ID:</span> <strong style="color: #0f172a;"><%= tokenData.userId || tokenData.user_id %></strong></div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="param-item"><span class="param-label">Code:</span> <%= code %></div>
            <div class="param-item"><span class="param-label">State:</span> <%= state %></div>
        </div>

        <% if (locals.error) { %>
        <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #fff1f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #991b1b; font-size: 0.85rem;">
            <strong>换票提示：</strong> <%= typeof error === 'object' ? JSON.stringify(error) : error %>
            <br><small>(注：若 Cowen Stream 先行完成了自动换票，此报错可忽略)</small>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="tip">
            <strong>Cowen 逻辑分离说明：</strong><br>
            在回调后，本 Demo 演示了 <strong>主动换票 (Active Exchange)</strong>：通过 Proxy 调用 <code>/oauth2/token</code> 接口。
            这样做可以直接在 Response 中同步拿到该租户的 <code>orgId</code>，方便业务系统进行账号绑定。
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px;">
            <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">注入用户 ID (可选 x-user-id):</label>
            <input type="text" id="input-user-id" placeholder="例如: 60006425377" 
                   style="width: 100%; padding: 0.6rem; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: monospace;">
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="btn-test" onclick="testApi('<%= locals.orgId || state %>')" class="btn-test">调用 (仅 OrgID)</a>
            
            <% if (locals.tokenData && (tokenData.userId || tokenData.user_id)) { %>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="btn-test-user" 
               onclick="testApi('<%= locals.orgId || state %>', '<%= tokenData.userId || tokenData.user_id %>')" 
               class="btn-test" style="background: #3b82f6;">调用 (带 UserID)</a>
            <% } %>

            <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">返回首页</a>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
            <label style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; font-weight: bold;">CIA 用户信息接口测试 (/accounting/cia/api/v1/user):</label>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="btn-cia-org" 
                   onclick="testApi('<%= locals.orgId || state %>', null, '/accounting/cia/api/v1/user')" 
                   class="btn-test" style="background: #6366f1; flex: 1; text-align: center;">CIA (仅 OrgID)</a>
                
                <% if (locals.tokenData && (tokenData.userId || tokenData.user_id)) { %>
                <a href="javascript:void(0)" id="btn-cia-user" 
                   onclick="testApi('<%= locals.orgId || state %>', '<%= tokenData.userId || tokenData.user_id %>', '/accounting/cia/api/v1/user')" 
                   class="btn-test" style="background: #8b5cf6; flex: 1; text-align: center;">CIA (带 UserID)</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="result-container" style="display: none; margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-top: 1.5rem;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16m-7 6h7"></path>
                </svg>
                调用结果 (JSON Response)
            </h3>
            <pre id="result-body" style="background: #0f172a; color: #38bdf8; padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.85rem; overflow-x: auto; line-height: 1.6; border: 1px solid #1e293b;"></pre>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        const COWEN_PROXY_URL = '<%= locals.cowenProxyUrl || "http://127.0.0.1:8080" %>';

        async function testApi(orgId, explicitUserId, path) {
            // Use explicitUserId if provided, otherwise fallback to input field
            const userId = explicitUserId || document.getElementById('input-user-id').value.trim();
            
            // Determine button to show loading state
            let btnId = 'btn-test';
            if (path === '/accounting/cia/api/v1/user') {
                btnId = explicitUserId ? 'btn-cia-user' : 'btn-cia-org';
            } else if (explicitUserId) {
                btnId = 'btn-test-user';
            }
            const btn = document.getElementById(btnId);
            const resultContainer = document.getElementById('result-container');
            const resultBody = document.getElementById('result-body');
            
            const originalText = btn.innerHTML;
            btn.innerHTML = `请求中...`;
            btn.style.opacity = '0.7';
            btn.style.pointerEvents = 'none';

            try {
                // DEFAULT PATH
                const apiPath = path || '/accounting/openapi/cc/book/findByEnterpriseId?queryType=BINDING_TO_THIRD_PLATFORM';
                
                // Construct target URL directly to Cowen Proxy
                const url = `${COWEN_PROXY_URL}${apiPath}`;
                
                console.log(`[Frontend Call] Directly calling Cowen Proxy: ${url}`);

                const headers = {
                    'x-org-id': orgId
                };
                if (userId) {
                    headers['x-user-id'] = userId;
                }

                const response = await fetch(url, {
                    method: 'GET',
                    headers: headers
                });
                
                const data = await response.json();
                
                resultContainer.style.display = 'block';
                resultBody.textContent = JSON.stringify(data, null, 2);
                
                // Animation effect
                resultContainer.style.opacity = '0';
                resultContainer.style.transition = 'opacity 0.5s ease';
                setTimeout(() => {
                    resultContainer.style.opacity = '1';
                }, 10);

                resultContainer.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('API Test Error:', error);
                alert('接口调用异常，请检查控制台输出');
            } finally {
                btn.innerHTML = originalText;
                btn.style.opacity = '1';
                btn.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        @keyframes spin {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
